<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Unlimitr ADR v5.1 — Atmospheric Diamond Refinery</title>
<style>
/* RETAINING ALL STYLES FROM v5 FOR CONSISTENCY 
   Adding specific style for the new Knowledge Base section
*/
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');
:root{
  --bg:#050709;--panel:#080d12;--panel2:#0b1118;--border:#111c26;--border2:#162333;
  --c:#00d4ff;--c2:#ff5722;--c3:#00e676;--warn:#ffab00;--danger:#ff1744;--gold:#ffc107;
  --purple:#e040fb;--teal:#1de9b6;--pink:#f50057;--lime:#c6ff00;
  --t:#b8d4e8;--t2:#3d5a6a;--t3:#1e3040;
  --mono:'Space Mono',monospace;--head:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;--body:'DM Sans',sans-serif;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--t);font-family:var(--body);min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden;}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(0,212,255,.011) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(0,212,255,.011) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:56px 56px;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;}
.wrap{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1560px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 20px;}

header{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:14px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border2);}
.hL h1{font-family:var(--head);font-size:3.2rem;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--c);line-height:1;}
.hL .tagline{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.5rem;color:var(--t2);letter-spacing:.14em;margin-top:4px;}

.tabs{display:flex;gap:2px;margin-bottom:12px;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;padding:3px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.tab{flex:1;min-width:66px;padding:6px 3px;background:none;border:none;border-radius:3px;font-family:var(--head);font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--t2);cursor:pointer;transition:all .16s;white-space:nowrap;text-align:center;}
.tab.on{background:rgba(0,212,255,.07);color:var(--c);border:1px solid rgba(0,212,255,.18);}
.tp{display:none;}.tp.on{display:block;}

.p{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:11px;}
.ph{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:7px 13px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:rgba(0,212,255,.01);}
.pt{font-family:var(--head);font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--c);}

/* Knowledge Base Specific */
.kb-container { padding: 20px; color: var(--t); line-height: 1.6; font-family: var(--body); }
.kb-section { margin-bottom: 25px; border-left: 2px solid var(--border2); padding-left: 15px; }
.kb-h2 { font-family: var(--head); font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
.kb-item { margin-bottom: 8px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.55rem; color: var(--t); }
.kb-item b { color: var(--c); }
.kb-box { background: var(--panel2); border: 1px solid var(--border2); padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 10px 0; }

/* RE-USING GRID AND OTHER v5 STYLES */
.g2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 360px;gap:11px;}
.sl{padding:11px 13px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;}
.sr{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;padding-bottom:5px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(17,28,38,.7);gap:8px;}
.sk{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.5rem;color:var(--t2);letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;flex-shrink:0;min-width:110px;}
.sv{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.56rem;color:var(--t);text-align:right;}
.pill{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.46rem;letter-spacing:.1em;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:2px;text-transform:uppercase; margin-left: 4px;}
.pill.r{background:rgba(255,23,68,.07);border:1px solid var(--danger);color:var(--danger);}
.pill.b{background:rgba(0,212,255,.07);border:1px solid var(--c);color:var(--c);}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

<header>
  <div class="hL">
    <h1>UNLIMITR ADR v5.1</h1>
    <div class="tagline">◈ INTEGRATED KNOWLEDGE BASE · 442 DIFFICULTIES SOLVED · 76% READY</div>
  </div>
  <div class="hR" style="display: flex; align-items: flex-end;">
    <span class="pill r">KNOWLEDGE INTEGRATED</span>
    <span class="pill b">V5.1 STABLE</span>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="tabs">
  <button class="tab on" onclick="showTab('overview',this)">Overview</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="showTab('kb',this)">🧠 Knowledge Base</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="showTab('difficulties',this)">Difficulties</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="showTab('financial',this)">Financial</button>
</div>

<div class="tp on" id="tab-overview">
  <div class="p">
    <div class="ph"><span class="pt">Project Status Summary</span></div>
    <div class="sl">
        <div class="sr"><span class="sk">Status</span><span class="sv" style="color:var(--c3)">76% Readiness — Targeting 85% build-start</span></div>
        <div class="sr"><span class="sk">Motto</span><span class="sv">"To our best knowledge we think (kinda)"</span></div>
        <div class="sr"><span class="sk">Core Goal</span><span class="sv">Atmospheric CO₂ to Gem-Quality Diamond</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.55rem; color: var(--t2); text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
    Switch to the "Knowledge Base" tab for the full technical summary and AI prompt data.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="tp" id="tab-kb">
  <div class="p">
    <div class="ph"><span class="pt">UNLIMITR ADR TECHNICAL MASTER FILE</span><span class="pb b">FOR AI CONTEXT INJECTION</span></div>
    <div class="kb-container">
      
      <div class="kb-section">
        <h2 class="kb-h2">1. PROJECT CORE & MOTTO</h2>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>Identity:</b> UNLIMITR Atmospheric Diamond Refinery (ADR).</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>Process:</b> Closed-loop, solar-powered conversion: CO₂ → CH₄ → Diamond.</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>Motto:</b> "To our best knowledge we think (kinda)" — Gaurav & Parth.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="kb-section">
        <h2 class="kb-h2">2. SYSTEM STAGES & SPECS</h2>
        <div class="kb-box">
          <div class="kb-item"><b>Stage 1 (Capture):</b> MOF Array (SIFSIX-3-Ni). 30 chambers. 90% capture efficiency. 95 m³/day capacity (7x headroom).</div>
          <div class="kb-item"><b>Stage 2 (Methanization):</b> Ruthenium-catalyzed Sabatier Reactor. Exothermic >280°C. 4.1:1 H₂:CO₂ ratio.</div>
          <div class="kb-item"><b>Stage 3 (Hydrogen):</b> Alkaline KOH Electrolyzer. 10 L/min H₂. Palladium membrane (99.999% purity).</div>
          <div class="kb-item"><b>Stage 4 (Growth):</b> 3kW MPCVD Reactor. University surplus sourced. ~4.5 ct/week raw growth.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="kb-section">
        <h2 class="kb-h2">3. THE "DIFFICULTY 442" PROTOCOL</h2>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>#420:</b> KOH Concentration Drift → <b>Fix:</b> Atlas EZO-EC conductivity sensor monitoring 20-30%.</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>#421:</b> RO Membrane Fouling → <b>Fix:</b> TDS meter on permeate line. Round Rock water ~350ppm.</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>#422:</b> Flex Space Heat Load → <b>Fix:</b> 2-ton (24k BTU) HVAC required for 3,500W continuous thermal load.</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>#315:</b> Catalyst Poisoning → <b>Fix:</b> Dual in-series TEPA traps. Replace every 45 days.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="kb-section">
        <h2 class="kb-h2">4. THERMODYNAMIC & ENERGY BALANCE</h2>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>Input:</b> 20x 550W Bifacial Solar Array (81 kWh/day average output).</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>Load:</b> 3,500W continuous (MPCVD 600W + Sabatier 800W + Chiller 1,500W + Fans 400W + Battery 200W).</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>Storage:</b> 19.2 kWh LiFePO4 rack (North wall placement).</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>Grid:</b> ~7-8% annual dependency for buffer/emergency only.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="kb-section">
        <h2 class="kb-h2">5. UNIT ECONOMICS</h2>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>Launch Total:</b> $43K (Best) | $47K (Likely) | $58K (Conservative).</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>Cost/Carat:</b> $1,977/ct (ADR) vs $4,520/ct (Conventional) — 56% advantage.</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>Revenue:</b> $5,300/mo (Stone + Surplus CO₂ sales + Surplus CH₄).</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>ROI:</b> 36-42 months for a single reactor setup.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="kb-section">
        <h2 class="kb-h2">6. CRITICAL SAFETY & PROVENANCE</h2>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>Anti-Static:</b> Mandatory for H₂ line work (0.017 mJ ignition energy).</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>N₂ Purge:</b> 2 min before every ESA cycle. Helium leak test before every growth cycle.</div>
        <div class="kb-item"><b>Provenance:</b> RPi/InfluxDB daily hash to Bitcoin blockchain via OpenTimestamps.</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tp" id="tab-difficulties">
    <div class="p"><div class="ph"><span class="pt">Difficulties Database</span></div><div class="sl"><div class="sr"><span class="sk">Total</span><span class="sv">442</span></div><div class="sr"><span class="sk">Unsolvable</span><span class="sv" style="color:var(--c3)">0</span></div></div></div>
</div>

<div class="tp" id="tab-financial">
    <div class="p"><div class="ph"><span class="pt">Financial Snapshot</span></div><div class="sl"><div class="sr"><span class="sk">Launch Range</span><span class="sv">$43K - $58K</span></div><div class="sr"><span class="sk">Net Profit</span><span class="sv" style="color:var(--c3)">$2,375/mo</span></div></div></div>
</div>

<script>
function showTab(name,btn){
  document.querySelectorAll('.tp').forEach(t=>t.classList.remove('on'));
  document.querySelectorAll('.tab').forEach(t=>t.classList.remove('on'));
  const t=document.getElementById('tab-'+name);if(t)t.classList.add('on');
  if(btn)btn.classList.add('on');
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
